title: GAY - BelAmi - Out At Last 3: Cocktails - Full movie
description:
Bel Ami's Out At Last 3: Cocktails




Bel Ami's Personal Trainers extraordinaire give new boys hands-on experience in having mind-blowing sex in front of a camera. "Out at Last 3" has 10 scenes which for one reason or another were not used in a "Personal Traners" video. George Duroy gives background information on each episode. The stamina of Bel Ami`s trainers mixing with the potent bevy of lissom beauties results in cocktails for two, three, four or more!

The Personal Trainers series of videos from Bel Ami are hugely popular not only among Bel Ami fans but also gay porn lovers in general. Unrehearsed, raw, uncut (pardon the pun!), they're an awesome insight in to how new Bel Ami models are trained, taught, and broken in by the experienced Bel Ami boys. It's so unbelievably hot watching veteran Bel Ami favorites show the new boys the ropes, and Out At Last 3: Cocktails is an awesome collection of some of the Personal Trainers episodes that were never releases as part of the PT series. If you like t:the Personal Trainers vids, this one you got to have!
